snippet.title: TRAXION 3000 -- Announcement Teaser
snippet.description: TRAXION 3000 is a cool new cave flyer game that lets you explore alien planets, fight enemies, and solve physics-based puzzles. This is the third entry in the TRAXION series and features all-new 3D graphics, tons of new gameplay features, as well as 2-4 player cooperative and competitive modes. Coming to Xbox, Playstation and PC.
